    "body": "Ah, I see the problem. A (hacky) way to make the `typecheck` config variable would be to run `tsc --noEmit` after `hardhat.config.ts` is loaded and abort if type errors were found.\r\n\r\nHowever, I am not sure whether it's worth doing that as my use case may be pretty rare.\r\n\r\nAlso, seeing this change as minor change might be confusing to some users(as it was for me). It looks more like a major(breaking) change to me.",
